      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a masterclass in naturally aspirated performance. At its heart lies the S54 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing for a razor-sharp 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a crisp ZF six-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock, ensuring surgical precision through the apex. This specimen is mechanically flawless, featuring a factory-reinforced rear subframe and a cooling system overhaul. The chassis remains incredibly rigid, and the factory finish retains its original depth and luster. A true showroom-grade icon for the discerning collector who demands peak mechanical synchronization.",
